Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.27,0:00:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.24,0:00:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打擾您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.82,0:00:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們能活著回來真不簡單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.45,0:00:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們雖然是活下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.42,0:00:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但度西斯卻已經…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.73,0:00:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道該從哪裡說起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.39,0:00:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照實說就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.20,0:00:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的頭腦裡現在一片混亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.87,0:00:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,諾齊亞…我們的故鄉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.97,0:00:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們或許再也回不去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.94,0:00:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們所僅有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.91,0:00:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下\N爸爸他們留下來的先鋒艇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.60,0:01:13.03,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,just keep on trying, keep on flying\N{\c&HFFBF00&}just keep on trying, keep on flying
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.10,0:01:16.63,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be the light\N{\c&HFFBF00&}I will be the light
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.71,0:01:23.98,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果說把黎明　當作是一個開始\N{\c&HFFBF00&}夜明けをひと　つの始まりとするなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.05,0:01:30.92,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果說現在就是來臨的時刻\N{\c&HFFBF00&}今が来るべき時だとするなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.99,0:01:35.55,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,與你的煙雲時代交響曲 飛向雲海的彼端 \N{\c&HFFBF00&}君とのCloud Age Symphony  雲の海の向こうに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.62,0:01:45.12,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,飛往光芒照射的方向\N{\c&HFFBF00&}光が射す方へ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.54,0:01:59.85,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah～是否可以遇見有如魔法的那瞬間？\N{\c&HFFBF00&}Ah～魔法のような一瞬に会えるのか？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.92,0:02:14.32,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,取代寒冷的黑夜  我倆展翅飛翔\N{\c&HFFBF00&}冷たい夜を引き替えに  二人は羽ばたいて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.40,0:02:24.43,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,在那盡頭  抓住了永恆…\N{\c&HFFBF00&}永远を掴む、その果てには
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.65,0:02:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H8dccf0&}身不由己\NFairy chess
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.27,0:02:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要進去囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.21,0:02:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長他想見妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.81,0:03:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳可是有報告的義務哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.64,0:03:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士他現在人在艦長室…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.05,0:03:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.38,0:03:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…不想去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.22,0:03:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想…現在去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.43,0:03:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒看到妳這種表情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.54,0:03:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士他人很溫柔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.58,0:03:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你出手還真狠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.72,0:03:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因為那個駕駛員的關係嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.79,0:03:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本來想找他談談的\N他卻根本不理我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.29,0:03:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大新聞哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.29,0:03:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說起來這可比諾齊亞淪陷\N或者度西斯瓦解更來得大條呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.26,0:03:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們那位小公主哦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.80,0:04:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的不騙你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.70,0:04:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從來沒看過\N小公主那個樣子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.44,0:04:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來她果然是跟克勞士…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.47,0:04:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.94,0:04:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你們閉嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.48,0:04:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通通閉嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.85,0:04:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蓋爾他當然是不高興囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.45,0:04:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為他早就看上了克勞士說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.12,0:04:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當心我扁你哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.85,0:04:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來那小子\N也不是個省油的燈嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.96,0:04:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託不要再隨便亂猜了好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.13,0:04:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣拉薇未免太可憐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.60,0:04:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫藍你太嫩了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.57,0:04:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要展開攻勢的話…就趁現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.11,0:04:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.38,0:04:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出來一下好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.21,0:04:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇，連克勞士妳也不理嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.99,0:04:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她什麼時候開始這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.32,0:04:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好一陣子了\N連回答都不回答一聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.86,0:04:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於諾齊亞的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.26,0:05:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也和妳一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.80,0:05:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛聽說的時候\N我也不知該如何是好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.53,0:05:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們一起努力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.80,0:05:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了努力也沒別的辦法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.54,0:05:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正在修理先鋒艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.57,0:05:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇妳不是常說嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.98,0:05:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論發生再難過的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.71,0:05:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要埋頭在機械裡就可以忘記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.28,0:05:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說我們一起修理好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.22,0:05:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起來修爸爸他們的先鋒艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.29,0:05:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇，我也在等妳哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.62,0:05:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.49,0:05:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給拉薇她一點時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.13,0:05:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.77,0:05:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.74,0:05:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你根本就沒搞懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.88,0:05:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下對於你讓四艘新建的\N烏爾班級戰艦沈沒一事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.91,0:05:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺十分的震怒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.92,0:05:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是陛下給你的處分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.62,0:06:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謹聽接旨吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.02,0:06:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,命即刻免除\N文生‧亞傑之烏爾班艦長職務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.60,0:06:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並立刻編入麥德賽侯爵麾下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.40,0:06:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討伐入侵諾齊亞的度西斯殘軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.77,0:06:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欽旨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.77,0:06:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,文生，雖然必須離開烏爾班號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.51,0:06:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過你不認為\N這才是一項光榮的任務嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.02,0:06:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,度西斯瓦解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.06,0:06:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銀之戰艦也隨著EXILE之鑰\N一起沈沒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.76,0:06:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搜索銀之戰艦的工作\N仍在持續進行中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.73,0:06:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在就斷定鑰匙已經消失\N會不會言之過早了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.30,0:06:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，一點也不會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.44,0:06:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.44,0:06:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基爾特公會憑藉EXILE來\N統治這世界的時代已經結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.91,0:06:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EXILE已成為過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.78,0:07:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,面對毫無威脅力的統治
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.32,0:07:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們安那托勒該做的事\N只有一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.99,0:07:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是消滅基爾特公會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.06,0:07:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下的意思是…要開戰了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.13,0:07:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快去準備吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.65,0:07:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.75,0:07:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安，拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.98,0:07:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.89,0:07:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於船艦的修復狀況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.65,0:07:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前已完成到\N足以啟航的階段了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.49,0:07:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,據各部門的報告，剩下的作業\N可以在出航後繼續進行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.56,0:07:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.73,0:07:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.30,0:07:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,動力啟動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.27,0:07:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全體人員，準備出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.37,0:07:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全體人員，準備出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.08,0:08:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,動力啟動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.51,0:08:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,齒輪傳動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.92,0:08:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,渦輪啟動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.93,0:08:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.90,0:08:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.03,0:08:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要一直站在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.16,0:08:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們要不要也來\N幫忙照顧一下這小傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.23,0:08:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,組件浮力壓已確保\N輪機準備OK
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.60,0:08:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舵機正常，航海準備完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.51,0:08:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有砲門全力發射沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.91,0:08:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦砲準備完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.28,0:08:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先鋒艇已完成固定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.71,0:08:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨時都可以出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.25,0:08:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左方搜敵，沒有敵蹤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.48,0:08:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,右方搜敵，同樣沒有敵蹤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.12,0:08:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.99,0:08:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,周遭沒有動力音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.26,0:08:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長，全艦已完成出發準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.33,0:08:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.83,0:08:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銀之戰艦出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.93,0:08:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩舷微速，開始上升
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.77,0:08:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始上升
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.73,0:09:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上升
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.19,0:09:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重新復出了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.06,0:09:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒弄錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.46,0:09:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.20,0:09:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已確認過克勞地亞反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.26,0:09:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是銀之戰艦沒有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.17,0:09:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前正在瑪琉山脈上空移動中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.40,0:09:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這事還有誰知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.07,0:09:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有我們和宰相閣下您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.51,0:09:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，別洩漏出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.01,0:09:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有關銀之戰艦的一切情報\N只能向我報告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.81,0:09:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千萬不可直接告訴陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.51,0:09:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.48,0:09:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屬下遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.72,0:09:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EXILE之鑰依然安在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.83,0:10:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下的判斷只會自取滅亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.86,0:10:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了避免開戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.53,0:10:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是得向公主殿下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.51,0:10:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是\N塔琪安娜跟我說的全部內容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.04,0:10:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她其實也是很辛苦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.31,0:10:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說，塔琪安娜和我們之間\N雖然有過一些過節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.05,0:10:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳能不能就原諒她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.59,0:10:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她說話的方式是衝了一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.56,0:10:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我想\N那也是因為她太認真的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.06,0:10:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.46,0:10:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很希望妳跟塔琪安娜之間\N能夠好好相處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.91,0:10:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.04,0:10:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.48,0:10:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士…對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.02,0:10:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我受不了和你待在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.25,0:10:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.45,0:10:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.22,0:11:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.43,0:11:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.14,0:11:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,視線良好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.48,0:11:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前方沒有任何飛行物體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.91,0:11:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長，請指示前進方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.38,0:11:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝基爾特總帥戴芬妮處前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.16,0:11:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.03,0:11:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗絲，妳什麼時候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.70,0:11:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳打算去哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.34,0:11:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是要把這還給克勞士而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.54,0:11:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.71,0:11:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望妳\N不要因為這件衣服而想太多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.65,0:12:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然他人的確是很溫柔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.35,0:12:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.35,0:12:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到拉薇那裡去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.16,0:12:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.73,0:12:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一整天沒見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.26,0:12:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是發生了什麼事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.06,0:12:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.53,0:12:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.57,0:12:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自從你和紅色的那個一起回來\N你就成了八卦焦點囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.94,0:12:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且你都不跟我玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.01,0:12:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你懂不懂啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.78,0:12:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的工作可是要監視我耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.18,0:12:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.91,0:12:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就好好幹活啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.38,0:12:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,休假已經結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.52,0:12:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這架先鋒艇\N長得和你那架一模一樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.69,0:12:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不這麼認為嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.99,0:12:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去過諾齊亞了是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.66,0:12:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去過諾齊亞了對不對\N鎮上現在情況怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.43,0:12:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你猜錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.00,0:12:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我在艦長房間裡找到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.47,0:12:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是亞力克斯的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.04,0:13:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啦，你居然沒發現啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.85,0:13:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真沒意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.88,0:13:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本來只想\N找個話題跟他聊聊的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.89,0:13:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進行搜敵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.02,0:13:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先鋒艇隊全體出擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.89,0:13:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.33,0:13:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞力克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.09,0:13:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.66,0:13:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先鋒艇隊出擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.27,0:13:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.93,0:13:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.41,0:13:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.25,0:13:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們幫妳\N另外準備了一架先鋒艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.49,0:13:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，恢復搭檔了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.99,0:13:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜，快一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.80,0:13:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.60,0:13:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士他今天不飛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.07,0:14:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才由我們兩個搭檔的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.30,0:14:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只限今天而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.01,0:14:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好閒哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.54,0:14:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也出去搜敵你說怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.11,0:14:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我猜迪奧殿下\N您姊姊也正在找您吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.32,0:14:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…還是算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.66,0:14:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全體先鋒艇出擊完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.50,0:14:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.94,0:14:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞力克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.91,0:14:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論真相是什麼\N你都能接受嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.05,0:14:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與其心裡一直有塊石頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.05,0:14:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我寧願知道真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.87,0:15:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我爸爸他們的照片\N會在你的房間裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.07,0:15:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你原以為是屬於你父親的\N那架先鋒艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.44,0:15:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實是我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.75,0:15:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天，告知你母親\N飛越大風暴區行動失敗的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.69,0:15:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.15,0:15:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和爸爸他們一起飛的人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.52,0:15:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.29,0:15:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是一條喪家之犬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.60,0:15:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夾著尾巴從大風暴區逃了回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.33,0:15:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把我最心愛的人\N就丟在了那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.97,0:15:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是說照片裡\N那個和你在一起的女子嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.48,0:15:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，我們曾互許了終生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.75,0:15:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有看到\N爸爸他們的最後一刻嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.09,0:16:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.66,0:16:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我大概到死都不會忘記吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.49,0:16:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.72,0:16:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她看著我們笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.76,0:16:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戴芬妮總帥…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.83,0:16:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.94,0:16:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這艘船之所以要對抗基爾特\N是為了復仇嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.75,0:17:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是除掉了它\N也不能改變什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.78,0:17:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不設法改變這個世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.88,0:17:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對抗基爾特就毫無意義了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.92,0:17:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,改變世界？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.32,0:17:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要能得到EXILE\N就可以改變這個世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.09,0:17:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EXILE！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.23,0:17:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我，EXILE究竟是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.87,0:17:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基爾特公會威權的憑仗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.44,0:17:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,足以顛覆這個世界的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.84,0:17:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得到那種東西…打算做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.98,0:17:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要親手來毀了它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.12,0:17:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你飛翔在天空的理由嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.32,0:17:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是一切的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.16,0:17:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不喜歡我的理念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.36,0:17:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你大可下船求去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.48,0:18:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.81,0:18:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘇菲亞公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.87,0:18:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，讓妳操心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.90,0:18:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我變成一個令人討厭的女孩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.71,0:18:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒這回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.51,0:18:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真傻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.14,0:18:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我只需要問他\N在沙漠裡發生了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.25,0:18:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要像平常一樣\N輕鬆的談一談就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.58,0:18:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我就是做不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.69,0:18:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士在我看起來\N就好像變了一個人似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.96,0:18:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我就是沒辦法控制自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.46,0:18:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜穿著\N克勞士衣服的身影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.20,0:18:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是一直在我腦海揮之不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.58,0:19:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宰相他希望我能登基
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.85,0:19:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在期待什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.65,0:19:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道妳是那種靠我的一句話\N來決定去留的弱女子嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.99,0:19:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好想一想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.70,0:19:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是為了什麼才登上這艘船的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.53,0:19:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不用去想就很清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.27,0:19:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳這髮型…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.07,0:19:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不適合戰艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.84,0:19:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.78,0:19:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我全都對克勞士說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.08,0:19:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過他似乎不打算下船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.82,0:19:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.84,0:20:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好香的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.84,0:20:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.11,0:20:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我擦了點香水想說換一下心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.91,0:20:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.42,0:20:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才在走廊上…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.85,0:20:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.89,0:20:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們聊一會兒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.82,0:20:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.57,0:20:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞力克斯他之前\N為何什麼都沒跟我說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.74,0:20:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他明明認識我，卻什麼都沒說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.81,0:20:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他只是冷眼旁觀\N我和拉薇在戰場上備受煎熬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.48,0:20:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他那麼做和殺了爸爸他們的\N基爾特公會有什麼不同呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.02,0:21:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長他內心也是很痛苦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.99,0:21:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不這麼認為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.96,0:21:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不是我把證據擺在他面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.69,0:21:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他恐怕打算永遠都不說出來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.46,0:21:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這才是我最不能原諒他的一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.20,0:21:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但即使如此\N你還是決定待在這艘船上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.84,0:21:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光是看著你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.91,0:21:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就可以知道\N你父親是個怎樣的人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.21,0:21:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長他可是很尊敬你父親的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.12,0:21:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘇菲亞妳又是為了什麼\N而登上這艘船的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.49,0:21:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.03,0:21:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不需要道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.73,0:21:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也很吃驚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.00,0:21:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從沒想過\N自己竟然是如此的軟弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.97,0:21:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘇菲亞妳絕對不是個軟弱的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.41,0:21:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你人真的很溫柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.15,0:22:38.98,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,黑夜的時光逐漸逼近\N{\c&HFFBF00&}夜の時間が迫り来る
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.99,0:22:46.02,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你離我如此接近感覺  卻好遠…\N{\c&HFFBF00&}あなたはこんな近く でも遠い…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.09,0:22:51.26,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你的憧憬是什麼\N{\c&HFFBF00&}何に憧れて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.33,0:22:57.10,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,心中想的又是誰\N{\c&HFFBF00&}だれを想うのか
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.17,0:23:02.84,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你奮不顧身的身影\N{\c&HFFBF00&}いのち賭ける姿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.91,0:23:11.61,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,有一種透明的美麗  令我噤聲無言\N{\c&HFFBF00&}透き通る美しさに 言葉を飲んだ
